commit fe44134e3cfaf6c22f8ff45bb43017d32b8b1663
Author: Olaf Mersmann <olafm@statistik.tu-dortmund.de>
Date:   2010-04-05 18:09:55 +0200

    Change the way fftw3 is located on UNIX like systems.
    
    Instead of searching for fftw3 using autoconf macros, rely on pkg-config
    to supply the necessary compiler and linker flags. This should fix a bug
    first reported by Prof. Ripley compiling the package on Solaris using
    the Sun Studio C compiler.

